dwinners.com/category/teen-choice-awards/2006/ |website=Awardsandwinners.com |accessdate=November 5, 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SM07jSoK |archivedate=September 5, 2014  }}</ref>\n|-\n| 2007 || Saturn Awards || [[33rd Saturn Awards#Best Television Actress|Best Actress in a Television Program]] || <ref>{{cite web |title=33rd Annual Saturn Awards nominees announced - Forbidden Planet Blog |url=http://www.forbiddenplanet.co.uk/blog/2007/33rd-annual-saturn-awards-nominees-announced/ |website=Forbidden Planet Blog |accessdate=2020-02-28 |date=2007-02-21 |first=Joe |last= Gordon|url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106061023/http://www.forbiddenplanet.co.uk/blog/2007/33rd-annual-saturn-awards-nominees-announced/ |archivedate=2016-11-06 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2008 || rowspan=2|Teen Choice Awards || [[2008 Teen Choice Awards|Choice Movie Actress: Comedy]] || rowspan=2| ''Forgetting Sarah Marshall''||<ref name=teen2>{{cite web|title=2008 Teen Choice Awards winners and nominees - The Envelope - LA Times |url=http://theenvelope.latimes.com/env-2008-teen-choice-awards-scorecard17jun17,0,2603341.htmlstory |accessdate=November 5, 2016 |date=September 12, 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080912051322/http://theenvelope.latimes.com/env-2008-teen-choice-awards-scorecard17jun17%2C0%2C2603341.htmlstory |archivedate=September 12, 2008  }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[2008 Teen Choice Awards|Choice Movie Breakout Female]] || <ref name=teen2 />\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2009 || Saturn Awards || [[35th Saturn Awards#Best Guest Starring Role in Television|Best Guest Starring Role in a Television Series]] || ''Heroes'' ||<ref>{{cite web|title=2008 Saturn Award Nominees |url=http://collider.com/2008-saturn-award-nominees/ |website=Collider |accessdate=2020-02-28 |date=2009-03-10 |first=Matt |last=Goldberg |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106123100/http://collider.com/2008-saturn-awa