am Awards]] || [[2011 Scream Awards|Best Cameo]] <small>(shared with [[Anna Paquin]])</small> || ''Scream 4'' || \n|-\n| 2012 || [[Gotham Awards]] || [[Gotham Independent Film Award for Best Ensemble Cast|Best Ensemble Performance]] || ''Safety Not Guaranteed'' || \n|-\n| rowspan=2|2013 || [[Alliance of Women Film Journalists]] || Best Animated Female || ''Frozen'' || {{won}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=2013 EDA Award Winners {{!}} Alliance of Women Film Journalists |url=http://awfj.org/eda-awards-2/2013-eda-award-winners/ |website=Awfj.org |accessdate=November 5, 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170107074730/http://awfj.org/eda-awards-2/2013-eda-award-winners/ |archivedate=January 7, 2017 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Streamy Awards]] || [[3rd Streamy Awards|Best Female Performance: Comedy]] || ''Burning Love'' ||rowspan=3 {{nom}} ||\n|-\n| 2014 || Teen Choice Awards || [[2014 Teen Choice Awards|Choice Movie Actress: Drama]] || ''Veronica Mars''|| <ref>{{cite web|title=Teen Choice Awards: The Complete Winners List |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/teen-choice-awards-2014-winners-724423 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2020-02-28 |date=2014-08-10 |first=Kimberly |last=Nordyke|url-status=live |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6UXnWYQsn |archivedate=2014-12-03 }}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 || rowspan=4|[[People's Choice Awards]] || [[41st People's Choice Awards#Television|Favorite Cable TV Actress]] || rowspan=2|''House of Lies'' || \n|-\n| 2016 || [[42nd People's Choice Awards#Television|Favorite Premium Cable TV Actress]] || {{won}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=People's Choice Awards: Fan Favorites in Movies, Music & TV - PeoplesChoice.com |url=http://www.peopleschoice.com/pca/awards/nominees/ |website=Peopleschoice.com |accessdate=November 5, 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ecsia6P4 |archivedate=January 18, 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2017 || [[43rd People's Choice Awards#Movies|Favorite Comedic Movie Ac